---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Audience Measurement & Verification | SDN"
  description="How SDN measures and verifies arena advertising audiences. People counters, Bluetooth mapping, demographic data, and attribution modeling."
  canonicalPath="/measurement/"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Audience verification</h1>
    <p>To accurately gauge facility audience size and impression counts, SDN employs three strategies.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="methods-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="methods-grid">
        <div class="method-card">
          <span class="method-number">1</span>
          <h3>People counter data sourced from multiple venues</h3>
          <p>Measures hourly visitor counts entering and leaving each facility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="method-card">
          <span class="method-number">2</span>
          <h3>Exclusive audience data</h3>
          <p>Proprietary audience data curated through third-party audits conducted by Pelmorex.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="method-card">
          <span class="method-number">3</span>
          <h3>Opto-Radio Bluetooth mapping</h3>
          <p>SDN deploys a network of strategically placed Bluetooth beacon devices within each arena.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Three Bluetooth beacons are installed in key locations per venue</li>
            <li>Resulting data is analyzed to build hourly impression models for each facility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mapping-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Mapping</h2>
      <p>We use proprietary mapping software to help clients optimize location strategy. This includes:</p>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature">Competitor proximity</div>
        <div class="feature">Distance analysis</div>
        <div class="feature">Drive-time modeling</div>
        <div class="feature">Coverage evaluation</div>
        <div class="feature">"Hot zone" analysis</div>
      </div>
      <p class="note">We match facility traffic with nearby retail traffic patterns to identify high-value opportunities.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="data-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Arima Data</h2>
      <p>We leverage the intelligence of Arima Data's platform, which aggregates 25 trusted data sources. This enables us to:</p>
      <ul class="data-list">
        <li>Build robust demographic audiences (similar to Vividata)</li>
        <li>Perform cross-media optimization</li>
        <li>Apply advanced location intelligence</li>
      </ul>
      <p>All to ensure we deliver sophisticated, trusted strategies to our clients.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="journey-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our user journey</h2>
      <p>We partner with Applied Post, a third-party provider with access to 40 million mobile devices. We have geo-fenced:</p>
      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <span class="stat-number">750</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Community sports properties</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <span class="stat-number">150</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Golf courses</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <span class="stat-number">200+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Points of interest tracked</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>We track visitor movement and index behavioural patterns by matching travel activity to these destinations.</p>
      <p>We can also determine visit frequency, daypart, dwell time, and length of stay. From this foundation, we build attribution models that demonstrate the effectiveness of each campaign.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Learn more about our measurement capabilities</h2>
    <p>Contact our team to discuss how we measure and verify your campaign performance.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn-white">Contact us</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .methods-section {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .methods-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .method-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--blue);
  }
  .method-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--blue);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .method-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .method-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .method-card ul {
    margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }
  .method-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .mapping-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .mapping-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .mapping-section > .container > p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .features-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .feature {
    background: var(--blue);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .note {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .data-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .data-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .data-section > .container > p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .data-list {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .data-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200, #e9ecef);
  }
  .data-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .data-list li::before {
    content: ">";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .journey-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .journey-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .journey-section > .container > p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .stat-box {
    background: var(--blue);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-box .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .stat-box .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
</style>
